%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20investor%20defends%20Laura%20Loomer%20on%20'Islamophobia'%3A%20'I%20had%20this%20face-to-face%20encounter...'%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129589631.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773577931000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129589676%2Cimgsize-103.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-origin-investor-defends-laura-loomer-on-islamophobia-i-had-this-face-to-face-encounter-%2Farticleshow%2F129589631.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Biggest%20Controversies%20in%20Oscars%20History%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129509158.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFor%20almost%20a%20hundred%20years%2C%20the%20Oscars%20have%20been%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20big%20night%3A%20the%20red%20carpet%2C%20the%20speeches%2C%20the%20golden%20statues.%20It%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20celebrating%20movies%20and%20the%20people%20who%20make%20them.%20But%20it%E2%80%99d%20be%20unfair%20to%20pretend%20that%20the%20show%E2%80%99s%20been%20just%20about%20a%20glamorous%20award%20night%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20just%20as%20famous%20for%20its%20drama%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20Every%20year%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%3A%20shocking%20mistakes%2C%20protests%2C%20statements%2C%20and%20speeches%2C%20some%20awkward%20encounters%2C%20or%20even%20a%20brawl%20or%20two.Over%20the%20years%2C%20some%20Oscar%20controversies%20hit%20on%20big%20issues%2C%20like%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20history%20with%20race%20and%20representation.%20Others%20are%20just%20plain%20weird%3A%20wrong%20winners%2C%20cringe%20moments%20that%20explode%20online%2C%20or%20that%20one%20time%20someone%20stormed%20the%20stage.%20And%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%20and%20the%20digital%20boom%2C%20these%20moments%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20disappear%3B%20they%20go%20viral%20and%20stick%20around%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Oscars%E2%80%99%20story%20forever.From%20Marlon%20Brando%20sending%20a%20protestor%20in%20his%20place%2C%20to%20the%20wild%20%E2%80%98Envelope-gate%E2%80%99%20blunder%20in%202017%2C%20to%20Will%20Smith%E2%80%99s%20headline-grabbing%20slap%20in%202022%20%E2%80%94%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20blips.%20They%20show%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20night%20is%20more%20than%20just%20about%20movies%20and%20their%20recognition.%20The%20ceremony%20always%20ends%20up%20reflecting%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20real%20tensions%2C%20values%2C%20and%20flaws.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773577435000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129509158%2Cimgsize-51864.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2F6-biggest-controversies-in-oscars-history-from-will-smiths-slap-to-envelope-gate-best-picture-mix-up%2Fphotostory%2F129509158.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20lauds%20Om%20Birla's%20leadership%20after%20no-trust%20motion%20fails%3B%20LS%20Speaker%20reacts%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lauded%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20for%20his%20composure%20and%20impartiality%20following%20the%20rejection%20of%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20him.%20Modi%20commended%20Birla's%20adherence%20to%20parliamentary%20decorum%20and%20his%20affirmation%20that%20no%20one%20is%20above%20the%20rules%2C%20reinforcing%20democratic%20traditions.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773577122000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129589573%2Cimgsize-838948.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-lauds-om-birlas-leadership-after-no-trust-motion-fails-lok-sabha-speaker-reacts%2Farticleshow%2F129589461.cms%22